articles.title: Social worker, Padma Shri awardee Sindhutai Sapkal passes away in Pune
articles.description: India News: PUNE: Renowned social worker and Padma Shri recipient Sindhutai Sapkal passed away due to cardiac arrest at a hospital in Pune on Tuesday.
